So what do you think?

00:06:39.669 --> 00:06:43.469
Should these dark chapters of Captain America’s
history be brought to the big screen?

00:06:43.469 --> 00:06:45.090
Or are they better left forgotten?

00:06:45.090 --> 00:06:48.620
Are there any dark stories of your own favorite
